apps.title: Bose Connect
apps.description:
Bose Connect unlocks the full potential of your Bose Bluetooth® Product.  

EASY ACCESS TO EVERYTHING
Get quick access to the key features on your products, like the auto-off timer, volume control, and battery readings. And it’s the easiest way to manage multiple Bluetooth connections. But that’s just the beginning.

SHARE THE MUSIC
MUSIC SHARE lets you listen together. Now two pairs of Bose® wireless headphones can share the experience - listen together, at the same time, while one of you DJ’s. New PARTY MODE lets you sync two SoundLink® speakers for double the audio…ideal for listening in two different places, and new STEREO MODE immerses you in music by separating the sound into Left and Right channels across two paired speakers for that amazing stereo experience.

GET THE MOST OUT OF YOUR HEADPHONES
CONTROLLABLE NOISE CANCELLATION on our QC®30 headphones lets you decide how much of the world to let in by adjusting the level of noise cancellation right in the app. And the built-in HEART RATE MONITOR for our SoundSport® Pulse headphones displays your heart rate clearly in the app.
 
AND SO MUCH MORE
From viewing product details to personalizing settings, get the most out of your Bose wireless products. It even downloads the latest software in the background and only installs it when you’re ready. See how our simple app can make all the difference.
 
 * NOTE * 
Bose Connect works with Bose Frames, QC®35, SoundSport® wireless, SoundSport® Pulse wireless, SoundSport® Free wireless, QuietControl™ 30, SoundLink® wireless II, ProFlight® headphones, and SoundWear Companion speaker, SoundLink® Color II, SoundLink® Revolve, SoundLink® Revolve+, SoundLink® Micro, and S1 Pro® speakers   
Some features may not be available for all products.
The Bluetooth® word mark and logos are registered trademarks owned by Bluetooth SIG, Inc. and any use of such marks by Bose Corporation is under license.

https://www.bose.com/en_us/legal/california_privacy_notice_of_collection.html

https://worldwide.bose.com/privacypolicy

apps.description:
Denison Municipal Utilities recently announced the release of the second generation of the company’s phone app called Mobile Customer Access (MCA).  This updated phone application builds on the customer’s ability to access their account 24 hours a day, seven days per week, 365 days per year.

In the past, utility customers could view balance information, make a payment, view statement and payment history, view usage graphs and access all their accounts at one time. apps.title: PointMan
apps.description:
PointMan is an innovative utility mapping software designed to precisely locate critical infrastructure both above and below ground. As a comprehensive utility mapping app, it serves professionals in various fields, such as: 

Construction
Subsurface Utility Engineering (SUE)
Municipalities

PointMan can also be used by individuals such as:
Home Owners
Individual Utility Locators
GNSS Hobbyist
Landscapers
Hikers
Hunters
And anyone else who is interested in accurately capturing precise location data

With PointMan's utility mapping technology, users can effortlessly capture, record, and visualize the exact locations of utility assets, ensuring unparalleled precision in data collection. Whether managing infrastructure projects or conducting field surveys, PointMan provides the necessary tools to achieve accurate utility mapping results.

The app seamlessly integrates with GPS/GNSS, cable and pipe locating equipment, and GPR utility mapping, enabling users to gather mission-critical data directly from the field. This integration ensures that every detail, from asset locations to depths and types, is accurately recorded. 

PointMan emphasizes being the ideal underground utility mapping software. Our app enhances utility data collection processes, allowing users to attach forms, sketches, and photos to mapped points, lines, or polygons for enriched data. 

Data security and accessibility are among PointMan’s top priorities. Data is collected and backed up in real time and integrated into a cloud-based mapping solution, accessible from any mobile device or desktop. This ensures that critical information is safeguarded and readily available for informed decision-making. 

PointMan is a utility detection software tailored for professionals who demand precise and reliable utility mapping solutions in their daily operations. By bridging the gap between the field and the office, PointMan transforms how field personnel capture and communicate data, ultimately empowering users to manage projects more efficiently and effectively.

Download PointMan now. PointMan’s GPS utility mapping is unmatched with the following capabilities:

• Data attributes: Captures detailed information, including type, depth, accuracy, and geospatial location of assets.
• Mobile mapping: Displays collected data on mobile devices for easy viewing and mapping.
• Data dictionary: Customizable data dictionary for comprehensive data management.
• Multi-feature collection: Allows simultaneous collection of multiple features.
• Real-time syncing: Syncs and communicates captured data in real time between field personnel and office teams.
• Data security: Ensures data security by backing up critical asset data during collection and integrating it into a cloud-based mapping solution accessible from any device.
• AWS Backed: Data is stored on AWS, ensuring reliability and security.

PointMan Plus:

• Attach photos and forms to any feature
• Configurable data dictionary
• Stakeout for points and lines
• Export multiple formats - KML, KMZ, SHP, CSV
• Geoid support
• Real-time datum translations

PointMan Pro:

Includes PLUS features and:

• View data from any web browser
• Backups & activity log
• SOC 2 compliant
• Site calibration
• Import shapefiles
• Field-to-finish in one step

In short, PointMan is the perfect software that provides precise utility mapping for construction, excavation, and similar critical projects. Experience the future of PointMan’s GIS mapping software. Download PointMan and elevate your utility asset management to new heights with our utility survey mapping capabilities and subsurface utility engineering mapping expertise.

Uninstalling PointMan:

If you are a Plus user, uninstalling will delete project data from your device. Please back up your project data before uninstalling PointMan. 

For assistance, contact support@pointman.com.

Install PointMan now!

apps.title: Silulumanzi
apps.description:
Our utility mobile app provides an intuitive and user-friendly experience, enabling users to manage their utility services efficiently and conveniently. With seamless navigation and a personalized interface featuring the utility’s branding, the app is designed to enhance user engagement right from the start.

Key Features:
•	Simple Sign-up and Secure Login: Users can quickly sign up or sign in using their mobile number or email, with OTP verification ensuring a secure process.
•	Home Screen Overview: The home screen provides various features, including fault reporting, navigation and account selection.
•	Dynamic Carousel: Utility staff can post important updates, promotions, or announcements to keep users informed and up to date.
•	Reporting a Fault: Users can report incidents, such as leaks or burst pipes, directly through the app. The location is detected automatically or can be entered manually. Non-registered users can also report faults via SMS OTP.
•	Payments: The app simplifies bill payments, allowing users to pay directly within the app using multiple payment gateways for flexibility.
•	Statements: Users can view detailed transaction history, including opening and closing balances, in both graphical and list formats. This allows for easy monitoring and management of finances.
•	Consumption Tracking: Track utility usage with graphical and tabular views of consumption over the last seven periods, including comparisons with the previous year.
•	Customer Service Applications: Users can update their customer details, attach relevant documents, and track the real-time status of their applications for changes to utility accounts.
•	Push Notifications and Messages: Stay updated with real-time notifications for billing, debt management, disconnections, and other important utility updates. Users will be instantly notified of new agreements or account changes.

With this app, managing your utility services has never been easier. Download today to take control of your utility accounts, report issues, and make payments—all from the comfort of your smartphone.

apps.title: Showbie
apps.description:
Used by over 3 million teachers and students worldwide, Showbie is the easiest and most effective digital learning app to personalise assignments and feedback on iPad.

DNA of Learning: Your Foundation for Student Success
Showbie supports the improvement of everyday teaching and learning by elevating four essential strands of effective classroom practice - direct instruction, independent practice, personalised feedback and real-time assessment - all in one platform.

Find out how easy it is to assign, collect and review student work from thousands of compatible iPad apps, or have your students complete assignments with Showbie’s built in tools. Provide rich feedback using digital ink, text and voice annotations right on images and PDFs, and then add your students’ best work to personalized digital portfolios that can be securely shared with parents.

WHAT EDUCATORS ARE SAYING
“Showbie is my number one can't live without app! It makes the iPad workflow process a breeze! I especially love how it works seamlessly with so many other apps.”
— Kristen Paino, Lead Technology Integrator at Avenues: The World School

“I don't need to convince my colleagues that they need to use this app — it sells itself. I like that it gives me the flexibility in how I choose to grade my student's work, especially with the voice notes feature. There is no single third party app that I would rather champion.”
— Suzanne Lustenhouwer, Teacher and iPad Coordinator, Apple Distinguished Educator

“I love that Showbie is so versatile that the youngest of students can use it independently, yet it is appropriate for older grades as well. The ease of use makes it a great workflow solution for classes with iPads.”
— Kristi Meeuwse, Kindergarten Teacher, Apple Distinguished Educator

KEY FEATURES FOR TEACHERS & STUDENTS
• Share work from thousands of compatible iPad apps in a few taps
• Use the pen tool and pin text notes directly on any PDF or image
• Gauge class understanding in real-time with minute-by-minute assessment
• Instantly differentiate assignments and materials to specific students
• Quickly distribute instructions and materials to your whole class
• Chat privately with individual students to provide timely feedback
• Record voice notes for verbal feedback or language exercises
• Quickly review and assess batches of student work and provide rich, valuable feedback
• Add student work to individual digital portfolios, or enable students to curate their own portfolios
• Invite parents to view their student’s work and keep them informed of classroom activity
• Can be used with any classroom subject
• Available in 18 languages

ENHANCED SHOWBIE PRO FEATURES
• Record and track grades as numeric scores or letter grades, along with qualitative feedback
• Provide richer feedback with more pen colours and line thicknesses, by typing on the page, or by pinning voice notes directly to student work
• Record longer voice notes and videos and upload larger files
• Lock assignments to control student access to documents and feedback
• Give parents complete access to assignments in the classes you choose

apps.title: Utility OX
apps.description:
Utility construction is tough work. Utility OX makes it run smoother, faster, and more profitable by putting every job detail, schedule, and resource in one place—accessible anytime, anywhere. Utility OX is purpose-built for utility and HDD underground contractors who are done wasting time with whiteboards, spreadsheets, and scattered apps.
No fluff. No feature clutter. Just the right tools your crews will actually use to keep jobs moving, downtime crushed, and profits protected.

Key Features:

Job & Project Management
- Manage every job from kickoff to close-out.
- View jobs on a map, calendar, or list with color-coded status indicators.
- Store all job details, drawings, permits, and documents in one place.

Task & Production Tracking
- Import project drawings as Task Sheets and draw tasks directly on them.
- Assign equipment, materials, and crews to each task.
- Crews log time, progress, and photos right from the field.
- Color-coded statuses show managers what’s done, in progress, or overdue.
- Completed tasks can automatically be added to Red Line drawings. Foremen can also add red lines manually for changes in the field.

Locate Ticket Management
- Organize all locate tickets in one dashboard with map or list view.
- Draw ticket areas on the map and track them with color-coded alerts.
- Attach approvals, white line photos, and clearance updates for compliance.

Bore Logging (HDD)
- Record pilot bores in real time with depth, pitch, and rod count.
- Export bore reports as PDF or Excel profiles for clients or inspectors.

Equipment, Tooling & Materials
- Complete fleet and tooling database with specs, photos, and availability.
- Search by capability (e.g., “reamer for clay”) to cut downtime.
- Schedule equipment, tooling, and materials to jobs or crews.
- NEW: Materials tab with unit costs, pricing, and allocation to jobs.

Crews & Crewmembers
- Keep crew rosters, skills, and certifications organized.
- View crew availability, job history, and productivity at a glance.

Time Clock (NEW)
- Let employees clock in/out and record breaks right from the app.
- Time can be tied to specific jobs or tasks for accurate costing.
- All time data flows into the Daily Production Report and can be exported for payroll and job costing.

Job Walk-Throughs
- Capture pre-job or progress walkthroughs with photos and notes.
- Use voice-to-text to quickly dictate notes in the field.

Production, Revenue & Job Cost Capture
- Track revenue, labor, equipment, and material costs per job.
- Compare bid vs. actual in real time.
- Visual dashboards show profit margins, progress, and cost codes.
- Export job financials to CSV/Excel for billing, payroll, or accounting.

Photo & Document Management
- Capture progress photos, bore logs, and completed work.
- Store permits, safety forms, and client documents alongside job data.

Soil & Dump Site Mapping
- Drop pins to record ground conditions and dump sites.
- Add details like soil type, disposal costs, or accepted materials.
- Entries are shared across all Utility OX users, so if you’re working in a new area you can see soil and dump site data others have logged.

Reporting & Insights
- Export production, cost, and revenue reports with a tap.
- Use data to refine bids, forecast resources, and improve margins.

HDD Calculators
- Built-in calculators for HDD planning and drilling parameters.

Why Contractors Choose Utility OX
- Made for utility contractors – not a generic construction app.
- Crew-first design – simple enough for the field, powerful enough for management.
- Single source of truth – keep jobs, people, and equipment in sync.
- Scales with your growth – from 2 crews to 20, Utility OX grows with you.
- Keeps downtime from eating profits – the Ox pulls your projects forward.

Utility OX: Tough Jobs Run Smoother with the Ox Pulling for You.
Download today and give your crews the power to keep every job on track.

raw_data.releaseNotes:

Same mission, tougher name. The app that knows how utility work really gets done just got a major upgrade.

New & Improved Features

- Name Change: Equappment → Utility OX — same team, same focus, brand-new look.
- Time Clock: Let employees clock in/out, track breaks, and tie time directly to jobs for accurate costing and payroll exports.
- Smarter Task Management: Import project drawings, create tasks directly on the sheet, log production, and automatically generate Red Line drawings and Production Reports.
- Materials Tracking: Add materials with cost and pricing fields, schedule them to jobs, and include them in cost reports.
- Cost & Revenue Tracking: Now capture job costs and revenue by equipment, materials, and crewmembers for real-time visibility into profit and performance.
- Daily Production Reports: Automatically compile logged hours, tasks, and photos into easy-to-export reports.
- Locate Ticket Enhancements: Draw ticket areas on the map and see color-coded status updates at a glance.

Why It Matters

This update makes Utility OX your single source of truth for production, costing, and reporting. Fewer spreadsheets. Fewer surprises. More pipe in the ground.

apps.title: Voice Recorder & Notes Pro
apps.description:
Voice Recorder & Notes Pro can meet all your recording needs and help you work more efficiently.

Transcribe all your meetings, interviews, lectures, and everyday voice conversations in real time.

POWERFUL RECORDING MODES: 
- Normal recording mode
This mode can start a professional recording easily, and a stable background operation makes your recording safer.

- Preset time recording mode
This mode can preset the start and end time of recording.

- Mix recording mode
This mode can mix recordings with selected audio.

- Voice-activated recording mode
This mode can record voice when you are speaking normally, and automatically pauses when your voice is below a specified decibel to get smaller file size.

- Bluetooth headset recording mode
This mode can start recording via connecting a Bluetooth headset.

AUDIO EDITING:
- Crop audio 
- Adjust volume
- Adjust pitch
- Adjust speed
- Insert audio
- Mix audio
- Split audio
- Merge audio
- Delete blanks
- Reduce noise
- Add markers

ADVANCED FEATURES:
- Passcode protect recordings
- Making ringtones
- Voice reminder
- Transcription
- Multi-segment loop playback
- AI file management

SHARE RECORDINGS:
Share audio by Email, Messages, AirDrop, iTunes, Albums, Facebook, Twitter, Whatsapp, Instagram, Snapchat, YouTube and more.

CLOUD SUPPORT:
Upload recordings to iCloud Drive, Dropbox, GoogleDrive, OneDrive, SoundCloud, Box and more.

apps.title: MyGVEC
apps.description:
GVEC is a cooperative dedicated to making a difference. Since 1938, we’ve been committed to empowering the people and communities we serve by providing unbiased information, responsive services, and valuable resources. Our mission is to enhance the quality of life through teamwork, vision, and unwavering dedication. Today, GVEC offers a diverse range of services including electricity, internet, and beyond-the-meter solutions, all while staying true to our foundational values. We invite our customers to download our free MyGVEC self-service portal app offering the ability to take care of your GVEC business or report an outage at your convenience, 24/7.

Additional Features:

Easily Manage Your Electric Account in 4 Easy Steps 

Bill & Pay—View your billing history, make an electronic bill payment and sign up for autopay.

Usage—Explore, compare, and monitor your usage to identify how to save money each month.

Settings—Keep your contact info updated and set bill alerts to receive by text or email.

Quick Links—Link to frequently used services including reporting an outage and staying up-to-date on important notifications.

For more information, visit https://www.gvec.org/.

apps.title: Swann Security
apps.description:
With Swann Security, everything is controllable via this single app.
Swann’s wired security systems, including all of our latest DVR and NVR series, now work seamlessly with wireless solutions such as Swann's new range of Indoor and Outdoor Wi-Fi security cameras. 

A list of products that work with this app can be found here: 
https://www.swann.com/us/apps

Please note that other Swann CCTV and IP camera models will not work with this app. This page will be updated as new compatible products are released.

Note: This app uses a data stream that will connect to your Swann system via 4G/5G or Wi-Fi. When using 4G/5G, the video from your Swann device may be considered "downloads" by your phone service provider and could contribute to any download limit your phone data plan may have. If you exceed any plan limits you may incur additional usage charges. Consult with your mobile service provider regarding the use of a video streaming app and how it may affect your plan. 

For assistance with this app, contact Swann Tech Support – tech@swann.com

An Apple iOS client for Partner Software's map application platform.

This platform, and its associated applications, are enterprise products designed for electric, gas, oil, and other utility organizations.

This app is only intended for use by Partner Software customers, and requires custom map data and configurations which are supplied by Partner's other products. Please visit our website for more information, and contact us if we can meet your needs.

There are two Apple iOS client apps for Partner. This app (Partner Maps) provides long-term support and more backwards compatibility. The other app (Partner Next) provides faster access to newer features.

apps.title: Hoke County Utilities
apps.description:
Hoke County Utilities recently announced the release of the second generation of the company’s phone app called Mobile Customer Access (MCA).  This updated phone application builds on the customer’s ability to access their account 24 hours a day, seven days per week, 365 days per year.

In the past, utility customers could view balance information, make a payment, view statement and payment history, view usage graphs and access all their accounts at one time.  With this the new release, utility customers will have access to many additional enhancements such as payment arrangement balances, programs they are enrolled in, enhanced usage graph, ability to sign up for notifications, report outages, view the utility outage map (if available), view the utility contact information, and view a message from the utility as they log into the app.  The customer can even log into the application with a touch of their finger or facial recognition by setting up biometric login.

raw_data.releaseNotes: Phone Number Entry improvements on registration, Logout crash prevention

apps.title: MMUA Connect
apps.description:
The MMUA app features utility and vendor members throughout the state. Consumers are able to locate contact details for their local utility services, while utilities can find details for vendors, stay connected with MMUA and more.

The association, members, and advertisers are showcased in this new user-friendly mobile app. The app is an indispensable tool for all users.

• Stay up to date on all the latest news in the industry.

• Easily view utility and vendor listings using the locator map.

• Quickly search for listings using our Directory feature.

• One touch access MMUA's Member Compass portal.

• Follow and participate in the MMUA Upcoming Events.

• Gain access to information on Government Affairs, Career Development and Safety Regulations in the industry.

The Minnesota Municipal Utilities Association (MMUA) is a nonprofit corporation formed in 1931. We serve hometown utility communities all over the upper Midwest, advocating for their needs, strengthening their operations, and empowering their leaders so that ratepayers receive reliable, affordable, and sustainable utility services.

apps.title: Ping - network utility

Features:
- Supports both IPv4 and IPv6
- Configurable TTL, timeout, send interval, and packet size
- Built-in library of favorite hosts
- Background mode (up to 30 seconds)
- Completely free, no ads

apps.title: Smart Summits
apps.description:
No events in the world offer a more productive environment to meet, share and explore ideas for Smart Utility success than the Smart Summits. Acquired by Endeavor Business Media in 2020, the Smart Summits  offers two world class Summits: the Smart Utility Summit (SUS) for Public Power Utilities, Rural Electric Cooperatives, and Investor Owned Utilities and the Smart Water Summit (SWS) for Water Utilities. The Summits have become mandatory events if you are seeking cutting edge information, powerful connections and innovative strategies regarding the future of the Smart Utility.

Get the 2022 Smart Summits Event Guide here today. Our mobile app is filled with all the info you will need for the all the 2022 Summits.

The Summits bring together Vendors representing the latest Technologies and Services for Smart Utility Solutions, as well as leading Executives from Public Power, Electric Cooperatives and Water Utilities in the United States. Using a distinctive, decision-making forum, every Attendee gets the chance to listen, learn and discuss emerging and current technologies.

apps.title: HSVUTIL
apps.description:
HSVUTIL is a free mobile app for Huntsville Utilities (Huntsville, AL) customers. Customers can use the app to log into their MyHU account to view usage and billing, manage payments, notify customer service of account and service issues, and receive special messaging from Huntsville Utilities. As a Public Utility, we answer only to the people we serve. Decisions are based on what is best for our customers. We do not pay dividends to stockholders. Instead, we provide lower prices to our customers. 

Additional Features:
Bill & Pay:
Quickly view your current account balance and due date, manage recurring payments and
modify payment methods. You can also view bill history including PDF versions of paper bills
directly on your mobile device. Make a payment now or schedule it for a future date.
My Usage:
View energy usage graphs to identify high usage trends. Navigate graphs quickly using an
intuitive gesture based interface.
Contact Us:
Easily contact Huntsville Utilities by email or phone. You can also submit one of the
predefined messages, with the ability to include pictures and GPS coordinates.
News:
Provides a convenient way to monitor news that may affect your service such as rate
changes, outage information and upcoming events.
Updated 3/7/2025
4
Service Status:
Displays service interruption and outage information. You can report an outage directly to
Huntsville Utilities.
Maps:
Display facility and payment locations on a map interface

apps.title: EE: Mobile, broadband & tech
apps.description:
THE EE APP
Welcome to the EE app – it’s all the good stuff in one place. Get complete control and all the help you need to manage your EE account.

What’s included?
The EE app gives you everything you need to bring your home to life and enhance your experience with us. The handy navigation makes it a doddle to find what you're looking for, and the new Manage hub is the perfect place to take control of all your EE products and services. The easy life is just a couple of taps away.

Maximise your allowance
Want to get the most from your allowance? No problem. Use Data Gifting to move data between your family’s EE plans quickly and conveniently.

WiFi Controls
If you’ve got a new EE Broadband package, you can fine-tune your connectivity with WiFi Controls—straight from the app. WiFi Enhancer lets you activate Work Mode and Game Mode, so you can be sure you’re maximising your connection’s potential. 

Parental Controls

apps.title: Speedify: Fast Bonding VPN
apps.description:
Boost your internet speed with Speedify, the only VPN that keeps you always online by joining multiple internet sources (4G LTE, 5G, Wi-Fi, Starlink, Satellite) into one bonded super-connection for reliable, uninterrupted online experiences.

Fix slow internet connectivity by using all available connections at the same time instead of just switching between them.

Tired of your audio and video buffering the second you step outside of Wi-Fi range? Speedify bonds your 4G, 5G and Wi-Fi connections together for seamless connectivity. It distributes your web traffic between them as necessary without missing a beat. Secure, easy to use, and compatible with all your favorite streaming services and apps, Speedify is perfect for:

– Livestream enhancement
– Dependable remote work
– Video call improvement
– Gaming performance boost
– Web browsing reliability


USE ALL OF YOUR 4G, 5G, Wi-Fi, AND STARLINK CONNECTIONS AT THE SAME TIME FOR SEAMLESS CONNECTIVITY.
Speedify's unique channel bonding technology lets you combine all available connections together to improve performance and reliability.

LINK UP WITH YOUR FRIENDS, FAMILY, OR COWORKERS VIA PAIR & SHARE.
With Pair & Share you can easily share cellular connections between multiple Speedify users on the same Wi-Fi network or personal hotspot. That means more stable connections on the road, at conferences and concerts, or while livestreaming. Grab your crew and create a super connection!

OPTIMIZED PERFORMANCE FOR FLAWLESS VIDEO CALLS AND STREAMING.
Speedify automatically prioritizes active audio and video streams, dynamically adjusting to network conditions so you don't have to deal with glitches or buffering.

TEST YOUR INTERNET CONNECTIONS BEFORE YOU LIVE STREAM.
Test the speed of your Wi-Fi, 4G, 5G, Starlink and satellite Internet connections to find your optimal resolution and frames per second. This way, your viewers won't experience low frame rates or drops in quality while watching your stream.

SURF SECURELY AND PRIVATELY–AS IT SHOULD BE.
We use the accelerated encryption from Apple's processors to deliver a fast, secure connection. Speedify VPN runs behind the scenes, encrypting the data transmitted for ALL of your apps, so you stay safe whether you're browsing, shopping, or livestreaming.

NO LOGS–YOUR DATA STAYS ON YOUR DEVICE.
Speedify doesn't just offer protection from outside snoops; we respect your privacy, too. At Speedify, we don't log the IP addresses of websites you visit or the contents of data sent or received through our service.

GET STARTED FOR FREE. UPGRADE FOR UNLIMITED ACCESS.
We give you your first 2GB of internet activity across all available connections (4G, 5G, WiFi and Starlink)  every month for free! And when you subscribe, you'll get unlimited usage and access to our servers for up to 5 devices at a time.

Upgrade to get Unlimited Access for just $14.99 per month or save 50% with an annual subscription of $89.99. Or, treat your entire family to faster, more reliable Internet. Speedify for Families plans include iCloud Family Sharing that lets you and five other family members share access.


TERMS
- Payment will be charged to iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.
- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
- Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal.
- Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.
- No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.
– Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.


Official Site: https://speedify.com/
Privacy Policy: https://speedify.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of Service: https://speedify.com/terms-of-service/

apps.title: Auto Price APP
apps.description:
Auto Price App - your reliable companion for vehicle sales. With our advanced AI, you can determine the daily market price for your car and thus set the optimal selling price. Say goodbye to uncertainties and achieve the best and most accurate price for your vehicle with our car value calculator! 

Features: 
- Daily updated market price: our app uses up-to-date data and intelligent algorithms to calculate the exact market value of your vehicle. With this knowledge, you'll always be up-to-date and confident that you're asking a fair and most accurate price for your car. 
- Optimal selling price (for dealers): Based on various factors such as predicted standing time, variable and fixed costs, resulting margin and return, matched with current market events, the Auto Price App recommends you the optimal selling price. In this way, you can optimally reach potential buyers and accelerate or optimize the sales process.
- Easy to use: Our app is designed to be intuitive and user-friendly. Simply enter the relevant information about your vehicle and the app does the rest, so you don't have to calculate complicated formulas or cumbersome estimates yourself.
- Trustworthy and accurate: rely on accurate estimates based on market data and advanced machine learning models. We pride ourselves on providing you with a mathematically best estimate that gives you significantly more confidence when selling your vehicle, compared to the so-called "experts".
- Save time and money: thanks to the Auto Price App, you no longer have to spend hours researching the market yourself or resort to expensive appraisers. Our app does everything quickly and efficiently, so you can focus on what's important - successfully selling your car, or talking to prospective buyers.

Optimize your car sale with the Auto Price app and get the optimal price for your car, taking into account all the complex influences mentioned above. Download the app today and determine your optimal / intelligent and therefore faster selling price.

apps.title: Varpet
apps.description:
Varpet is a single platform for In-home services where you can meet your expectation for everyday living as we establish the connection between individuals seeking services and service providers at their fingertips and then at their doorsteps. Varpet Services is a marketplace for home and professional services where you can find and get every type of service. You can book a wide range of services, delivered by well-qualified & background-checked masters. Varpet is for simplifying your everyday living. All you have to do is place a request, sit back and relax.  
Varpet brings the best of experts in-home services, Home maintenance, Appliance repairs, Utility services, Lifestyle services, Beauty services, Medical services, Repair & Maintenance, and other professional service experts.
With a large service provider base, on-time services, flexible pricing, and service guarantee, Varpet ensures that you get the best of services.

Features:
•	Transparent and affordable pricing and policies. Pricing is available on all services upfront. Every job is closed via mobile app and an invoice is generated for every completed job.
•	Transparency in Reviews and Ratings․ After the job is closed the client is able to rate the master. Also, the customers can see the ratings of the masters.
•	Convenient booking. Pick the service you want, and select the date, time, and place of visit. Once the case is booked, our app instantly finds a verified and reliable home master in your locality.
•	Reliable and Verified masters. Every master on Varpet app goes through a complete background verification process before being on-boarded on the platform. Once the master’s business, authenticity, and skill are confirmed, only then do we activate him and assign jobs.
•	Possibility to make free calls to the master who accepted your order. You can make free calls through the app, you can also make calls by your service provider.
•	It is possible to cancel the master’s service who has accepted your order and look for another master.
•	Place your order specially for your preferred master.
•	Users’ Help, from where You can call or message the support center, You can also contact via Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, and Messenger. 
•	In the FAQ sub-section You can find the answers to the most common questions.
•	The News section provides the latest updates and news.

How does it work?
•	Download the app and register,
•	Pick the service you want,
•	Select the Date, Time, and Place of visit,
•	Once the case is booked, our app instantly finds a verified and reliable master in your locality,
•	Master visits your home as scheduled and completes the job,
•	You pay the Master via cash and rate him/her on his performance.

The app uses only little spaces on your device. Constant updates and additions of new features will make Your life more comfortable. Varpet is knowledgeable, quick to respond, and always has a solution for Your needs.

Contact us:   
Phone: +374 96 999944       
E-mail: support@varpet.com
Facebook - http://bit.do/eDC3E
Twitter - http://bit.do/eDC3k
Instagram - http://bit.ly/instavarpet
Web site: https://varpet.com

apps.title: Link2Valves
apps.description:
To keep your water system infrastructure working smoothly, it is imperative to track the maintenance status of your control valves. The Cla-Val Link2Valves™ asset management platform is designed specifically for the needs of water utilities to ensure your equipment is being serviced routinely. Link2Valves delivers an intuitive and user-friendly design that provides clear and easy access to your asset information, helping maximize service and maintenance efficiencies for your automatic control valves and other water system assets.

Access our secure portal from your desktop or mobile device to gain insights across your water system assets to help you:

 • Determine which valves require preventative maintenance
 • Minimize downtime
 • Maintain and optimize your water system assets
 • Keep your operations compliant, operational and economical

The Link2Valves app allows you to view, edit, and create new valve assets with all the details of your equipment, including part numbers, setpoints, photos, and maintenance activity records. Your data is synced with the Link2Valves website, providing a complete service history, exact valve location, configuration options, and graphical indication of which valves may require attention, whether in the field or in the office.

Link2Valves is absolutely free for all users. We offer this as a no-cost service to our valve users as a tool to assist them in keeping their control valves in good health.

Please visit our website for more details: https://www.cla-val.com

apps.title: HP
apps.description:
The go-to app for your HP devices. Set up your new printer, personalize your experience, print, scan, and contact support—all in one place. 

Formerly HP Smart, the new HP app[1] offers you more ways to get more from your HP devices. 

Easy Setup, Wherever You Are  
New device? No problem. Get up and running fast with a guided setup that does the heavy lifting for you. Once you are ready to go, you can manage your HP printer and computer and stay on top of the essentials, like checking your ink levels. 

Make the Most of Your Device 
Stay informed with top recommendations. Plus, you can adjust your device settings and discover HP products that match your needs—it is all about making your tech work just the way you like it. 

Print and Scan, On Your Time 
Print a school form from the kitchen or a last-minute birthday card. Even, scan receipts in seconds and send it straight to your email. Whether you are at home or at the office, completing your print tasks is a click away. 

Instant Help Whenever You Need It 
When something goes wrong, help is right there—make a quick call, message live chat or find answers in the app[1]. You’ll be back to what matters before you know it. 

 
But wait, your experience just gets better and better! 

• Unlock a world of creativity with HP Printables[2]. Explore tons of cards, coloring pages, educational worksheets, and fun crafts projects. 

• Adjust and edit your documents before you hit print. 

• Set up custom shortcuts for print tasks you use often. 

• Automatically correct images, name files, flatten pages, extract text, and scan multiple pages at the same time with the HP app.[3] 

• Get a notification when your printer is low on ink or paper and easily order more to keep printing uninterrupted. 

We're always adding cool new features to the app. Make sure you turn on auto-updates, so you don't miss all the latest improvements!  

Disclaimers

1. HP Smart and myHP are now the HP app, available for download on macOS devices; and for iOS mobile phones and iPads. The HP app requires download available at www.hp.com/hp-app. Not all HP devices, services, apps are available in the HP app. Certain features are available in English language only, and may vary by printer and PC model/country, and between desktop/mobile applications. HP reserves the right to introduce charges for use of select HP app functionality. Internet access required. HP account required for full functionality. Fax sending capability only. Live chat and phone support are available during business hours and varies by country. Chat service is localized in supported regions, and where not supported, will default to English. Supported conferencing features vary by device and device configuration. For complete Terms of Service see: www.hp.com/hp-app-terms-of-use. 

2. Printables are for personal use only and may not be distributed for any commercial purpose. 

3. Choose HP+ at setup to activate benefits. HP+ requires an HP account, ongoing connection to the internet, and the use of only Original HP ink for the life of the printer. More at hp.com/plus

raw_data.releaseNotes: HP Smart is now HP app! We redesigned the app for a simpler, more convenient experience. You can now get support for more HP products — not just your printer. This includes HP laptops, desktops, pens, docks, and more.

apps.title: Sylacauga Utilities Board
apps.description:
Sylacauga Utilities Board recently announced the release of the company’s phone app called Mobile Customer Access (MCA).  This phone application builds on the customer’s ability to access their account 24 hours a day, seven days per week, 365 days per year.

In the past, utility customers could view balance information, make a payment, view statement and payment history, view usage graphs and access all their accounts at one time.  With this the new release, utility customers will have access to many additional enhancements such as payment arrangement balances, programs they are enrolled in, enhanced usage graph, ability to sign up for notifications, report outages, view the utility outage map (if available), view the utility contact information, and view a message from the utility as they log into the app.  The customer can even log into the application with a touch of their finger or facial recognition by setting up biometric login.

apps.title: charging play
apps.description: A charging animation software with IOS 14 shortcut command automation is used. When the mobile phone is connected to the data line or the wireless charging panel is placed, the program will automatically start and turn on the charging animation display. When the data line is pulled out or removed from the wireless charging panel, the program will automatically exit, which is convenient and practical.   the program will automatically calibrate the decimal data of charging percentage according to your charging data, and automatically learn to calibrate so that the device can understand you better   the software needs to cooperate with IOS 14 shortcut command automation to achieve a perfect experience. apps.title: Evernote - Notes Organizer
apps.description:
Capture ideas when inspiration strikes. Bring your notes, to-dos, and schedule together to tame life’s distractions and accomplish more—at work, at home, and everywhere in between. 

Evernote syncs to all your devices, so you can stay productive on the go. Tackle your to-do list with Tasks, connect your Google Calendar to stay on top of your schedule, and see your most relevant information quickly with a customizable Home dashboard. 

---

“Use Evernote as the place you put everything… Don’t ask yourself which device it’s on—it’s in Evernote” – The New York Times

“When it comes to taking all manner of notes and getting work done, Evernote is an indispensable tool.” – PC Mag

---

CAPTURE IDEAS
• Write, collect, and capture ideas as searchable notes, notebooks, and to-do lists.
• Clip interesting articles and web pages to read or use later. 
• Add different types of content to your notes: text, docs, PDFs, sketches, photos, audio, web clippings, and more.
• Use your camera to scan and organize paper documents, business cards, whiteboards, and handwritten notes.

GET ORGANIZED
• Manage your to-do list with Tasks—set due dates and reminders, so you never miss a deadline.
• Connect Evernote and Google Calendar to bring your schedule and your notes together.
• See your most relevant information instantly on the Home dashboard.
• Create separate notebooks to organize receipts, bills, and invoices.
• Find anything fast—Evernote's powerful search can even find text in images and handwritten notes.


ACCESS ANYWHERE
• Sync your notes and notebooks automatically across any computer, phone, or tablet.
• Start work on one device and continue on another without missing a beat.

EVERNOTE IN EVERYDAY LIFE
• Keep a journal to keep your thoughts organized. 
• Go paperless by scanning receipts and important documents.

EVERNOTE IN BUSINESS
• Keep everyone up to date by capturing meeting notes and sharing notebooks with your team.
• Bring people, projects, and ideas together with shared Spaces. 

EVERNOTE IN EDUCATION
• Keep track of lecture notes, exams, and assignments so you don’t miss important details.
• Create notebooks for each class and keep everything organized.

---

Also available from Evernote:

EVERNOTE PERSONAL
• 10 GB of new uploads each month
• Unlimited number of devices
• Create and manage tasks
• Connect one Google Calendar account
• Access your notes and notebooks offline

EVERNOTE PROFESSIONAL
• 20 GB of new uploads each month
• Unlimited number of devices
• Create, manage, and assign tasks
• Connect multiple Google Calendar accounts
• Access your notes and notebooks offline
• Home dashboard - Full customization

--

Price may vary by location. Subscriptions will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account. Where applicable, your subscription will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Subscriptions may not be cancelled for refund except as provided in Evernote's Commercial Terms. Manage your subscriptions in Account Settings after purchase.

---

Terms of Service: https://evernote.com/legal/tos.php
Commercial terms: https://evernote.com/legal/commercial-terms

apps.title: Gaia: Streaming Consciousness
apps.description:
Gaia is your guide to conscious life. We’re dedicated to finding and creating informative films, original shows, practices, and documentaries that aren’t available through mainstream media. We look to elevate your awareness through enlightening content covering personal transformation, ancient origins, alternative medicine, and much more. Gaia is your window into a new way of viewing the world.

Gaia is the premier streaming platform where the world’s top thought leaders and teachers share knowledge and expertise to empower your conscious awakening. Seek your truth with our library of 8,000+ videos, films, documentaries, series, and live events aimed at answering life’s biggest questions while at the same time helping you navigate everyday complexities.

Stream videos on personal transformation, yoga, meditation, and more with Gaia as your guide to holistic mental health and spirituality. Use our videos to discover new perspectives today and track your yoga practice and meditative activity in your Apple health app. Gaia is a complete resource for personal enlightenment, mindful living, and universal consciousness.

Whether you want to enjoy a mindful yoga practice, practice deep meditation, or you’re seeking truth through metaphysics, fuel the pursuit of your highest potential with Gaia.
 
GAIA FEATURES

COMPELLING CONTENT THAT BREAKS BOUNDARIES
- Discover ancient history, metaphysics, yoga, meditation, alternative health and more
- Explore videos according to your taste and let your conscious journey begin
- Enjoy exclusive content and videos that push the boundaries of tradition and encourage different ways of viewing the world
- Learn more about spirituality and explore the world of astral projection, tarot cards, and hypnosis
 
EXPLORE A NEW WAY OF THINKING
- Join thought leaders in exploring topics like lucid dreaming, spiritual healing, and aura health
- Dive into a vast library of content that will have you questioning what you know about the world
- Explore the mysteries of metaphysics, extraterrestrial life, astrology, and more
- Navigate the intricacies of topics such as plant medicine, hypnosis, and energy healing
 
YOUR PATH TO HOLISTIC & SPIRITUAL WELLNESS
- Access the world’s best teachers and spiritual luminaries to guide you on your self care path
- Enjoy exercises for personal growth, including yoga nidra, meditation, mindful breathing, and more
- Navigate the world’s largest conscious media network for a deep mental, physical, and spiritual connection
- Learn the anxiety relief benefits of intermittent fasting, unblocking chakras and other holistic health techniques
 
Gaia supports healthKit, allowing you to track your Yoga and Meditation activity in the Apple Health app.

Use an existing login or purchase an auto-renewing subscription with your iTunes account to get access to Gaia. We offer a 7-day free trial with our $13.99 monthly plan & $119 annual plan, and a Gaia+ streaming plan for $299 annually without a free trial. Prices may vary by region. A single account grants you access to Gaia on supported devices, TVs, and the Web.

Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's iTunes Account Settings after purchase - No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period

apps.title: State Farm®
apps.developer: State Farm Mutual Automobile Insurance Company
apps.description:
With the award-winning State Farm app, you can manage your insurance policies and other products, request roadside assistance, file and track claims and much more. 

Drive Safe & Save® is on the move! 
    •  We’re moving all the great features of our safe driving discount program — Drive Safe & Save — into the State Farm app. 
    •  If you’re enrolled in the program, we’ll email the first person listed on your auto policies when it’s time to start using the State Farm app to access your Drive Safe & Safe details.
    •  If you’re already using the Drive Safe & Save app, you won’t lose any of your info.

IMPORTANT: Drive Safe & Save terms of use, including precise location data collection and sharing, only apply to customers who set up Drive Safe & Save and enable specific permissions on their mobile devices. 

View and manage your insurance policies.
    •  Quickly pay your insurance bill — even with Apple Pay.
    •  View your insurance card and add it to Apple Wallet. 
    •  View your insurance policies and coverage details.

We’re here to help when you have a claim. 
    •  File a vehicle, property or vehicle glass claim.
    •  Track the status of your claim through every step.
    •  Get claim status notifications.
    •  Get roadside assistance with tire changes, dead batteries, stuck vehicles and more.
    •  Search for repair shops.

More convenient features: 
    •  Get personalized reminders and notifications when you log in.
    •  Ask Siri to view your insurance card or claims with our shortcuts.
    •  Log in with Touch ID, Face ID or a PIN.
    •  Need technical assistance? Send us a message on your time with our messaging feature.
    •  View details about your financial products.
    •  Help topics are available in the app when you need them.
    •  Learn about other products State Farm offers.

apps.title: Google
apps.description:
Download the Google app to stay in the know about things that matter to you. Try AI Overviews, find quick answers, explore your interests, and stay up to date with Discover. The more you use the Google app, the more it’s tailored to you.

Feature highlights:

• Image Search: See something you like? Snap a photo and discover where to shop for it, find related images, and more. Refine your camera searches by adding words – whether you want those shoes but in ‘blue’, or want to learn how to ‘repair’ that broken bit on your bicycle.
• Hum to Search: Can't remember the name of that song? Hum the tune and the Google app will identify it for you.
• Discover: Stay up-to-date on topics that matter to you. Get personalized news, articles, and videos based on your interests and search history.
• Try AI Overviews: We’re making search smarter and simpler with generative AI. Try searching things like ‘how to cut onions without crying’ or ‘how to fix a broken zipper’ and AI Overviews will find what you’re looking for in faster, easier ways.
• Google Search Widget: Search from your home screen or lock screen with the new Google widget. Choose from 2 widgets, giving you a quick search bar in both sizes, and shortcuts to choose how you Search with Lens, Voice, and Incognito in the medium size widget.

Search what you see with Google Lens:

• Use your camera to identify what you’re looking at. Identify plants and animals, translate text in real-time, find similar products to buy, and even solve math problems with step-by-step guides.
• Translate over 100 languages on things like road signs when you travel, menus, and more by pointing your camera at text.
• Reverse image search: Find the source, similar photos, and related information for any image.
• Socratic app functionalities like step-by-step homework help on math, physics and word problems, and testing your knowledge with Questions and Answers are now fully supported within the Google app.


Get personalized updates in Discover:

• Stay in the know about topics that interest you.
• Start your morning with weather and top news.
• Get real-time updates on sports, movies, and events.
• Know as soon as your favorite artists drop new albums.
• Get stories about your interests and hobbies.
• Follow interesting topics, right from Search results.

Search safely and securely:

• All searches in the Google app are protected by encrypting the connection between your device and Google.
• Privacy controls are easy to find and use. Tap your profile picture to access your menu and delete recent search history from your account with one click.
• Search proactively filters webspam to help ensure that you see safe, high-quality results.


Learn more about what the Google app can do for you: https://search.google/

Privacy policy: https://www.google.com/policies/privacy

Your feedback helps us create products you'll love. Join a user research study here:
https://goo.gl/kKQn99

raw_data.releaseNotes:
• Bug fixes and performance improvements.

We are always working to make the app faster and more stable. If you are enjoying the app, please consider leaving a review or rating!

apps.title: NJUS Nome Joint Utility System
apps.description:
Nome Joint Utility Systems Brown County recently announced the release of the second generation of the company’s phone app called Mobile Customer Access (MCA).  This updated phone application builds on the customer’s ability to access their account 24 hours a day, seven days per week, 365 days per year.

In the past, utility customers could view balance information, make a payment, view statement and payment history, view usage graphs and access all their accounts at one time.  With this the new release, utility customers will have access to many additional enhancements such as payment arrangement balances, programs they are enrolled in, enhanced usage graph, ability to sign up for notifications, report outages, view the utility outage map (if available), view the utility contact information, and view a message from the utility as they log into the app.  The customer can even log into the application with a touch of their finger or facial recognition by setting up biometric login.

apps.title: GoodayOn
apps.description:
GoodayOn's gig workers offer a range of services, including house cleaning, laundry, cooking, plumbing, electrical repairs, painting, and carpentry, among others. Customers can browse and select from a list of available services and gig workers nearby. Once a customer has selected a gig worker, they can communicate with them directly through a phone call to confirm details, discuss any additional requirements, and arrange for the service to be provided.

GoodayOn's digital platform provides a range of benefits for both customers and gig workers. Customers can easily access a range of services in one place, with the assurance of quality, reliability, and affordability. Gig workers can create a digital presence for themselves, access a wider market for their services, and manage their bookings easily through the platform. GoodayOn's services are designed to create job opportunities, promote entrepreneurship, and contribute to the economy in Ethiopia, where unemployment rates are critically high.
